# Cloudflare Pages redirects (https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/)
# Format:  /source  /destination  STATUS    (one rule per line, first match wins)
#
# Pages already handles these automatically, so they need NO rules here:
#   - pretty URLs:      /about     serves    /about.html
#   - trailing slashes: /about/    redirects to  /about
#
# 301 = permanent (passes SEO link equity). Targets use pretty URLs (no .html)
# to match the canonical tags and avoid a second hop. Sources from Search Console.

